# Rules

## Overview

Portfolio-v7 is a website built with Astro, React (where needed for interactivity), TailwindCSS, and Sanity CMS. The Sanity CMS is in a different repo.

## Folder Structure

```
portfolio-v7/
├── public/             # Static assets (served as-is)
├── src/                # Main source code
│   ├── assets/         # Assets to be processed by Astro's build
│   ├── components/     # Reusable components
│   ├── layouts/        # UI layouts
│   ├── lib/            # Shared utilities & data constants
│   ├── pages/          # File-based routing
│   ├── sanity/         # Sanity CMS integration helpers
│   ├── scripts/        # Client-side JavaScript effects
│   ├── styles/         # Global styles & Tailwind
│   └── utils/          # Pure utility functions
├── astro.config.mjs    # Astro configuration
├── package.json        # Dependencies & scripts
├── pnpm-lock.yaml      # pnpm lockfile
├── tsconfig.json       # TypeScript config
```

## Commands

```
pnpm dev                # Start local dev server with hot reload
pnpm build              # Build production site to dist/
pnpm preview            # Preview production build locally — PREFER THIS OVER pnpm build
pnpm astro              # Run Astro CLI commands directly
```
